@startuml driver_seat_cmd_to_seat_drv_position_comfort_signal_flow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

title Driver Seat Cmd To SEAT DRV Position Comfort Signal Flow\n(seat-control command + vehicle state -> driver seat position / heat / ventilation state)

participant "Seat-control bus" as SeatCtl #F4F7FB
participant "Vehicle state bus" as Veh #E8F0FE
participant "SEAT_DRV\ndriver-seat owner" as SeatDrv #E8F7E8
participant "Driver-seat state bus" as SeatBus #FFF4CC
participant "Observers /\ncomfort readers" as Obs #FCE8FF

== Driver Seat Inputs ==

SeatCtl -> SeatDrv : frmSeatControlMsg\nDriverSeatCmd / SeatHeatLevel / SeatVentLevel
Veh -> SeatDrv : frmVehicleStateCanMsg\ngDriveState
activate SeatDrv
SeatDrv -> SeatDrv : seatCtrlInputStale =\nethIsRecentTick(gSeatCtrlRxMs, 300)
SeatDrv -> SeatDrv : vehicleInputStale =\nethIsRecentTick(gVehicleRxMs, 300)
SeatDrv -> SeatDrv : if seat-control stale then\nseatCmd = 0 / heat = 0 / vent = 0
SeatDrv -> SeatDrv : if vehicle stale then\ndriveState = 3
SeatDrv -> SeatDrv : position changes only when\ndriveState == 0
SeatDrv -> SeatDrv : applySeatDelta() moves\nSeatDrvPos by +/-5 per command step
note right of SeatDrv
Representative gating inputs
- DriverSeatCmd
- SeatHeatLevel
- SeatVentLevel
- gDriveState
end note

== Driver Seat Publish ==

SeatDrv -> SeatBus : frmSeatDrvStateMsg\nSeatDrvPos / SeatDrvHeatLvl / SeatDrvVentLvl
note right of SeatDrv
Representative outputs
- SeatDrvPos
- SeatDrvHeatLvl
- SeatDrvVentLvl
end note

== Downstream Visibility ==

SeatBus -> Obs : driver-seat comfort visibility /\nseat and cabin observers
deactivate SeatDrv

note over SeatCtl, Obs
Representative runtime chain
1. Driver seat-control command and vehicle state reach SEAT_DRV
2. SEAT_DRV applies freshness gates and parked-only motion rule
3. SEAT_DRV updates seat position and comfort levels
4. SEAT_DRV publishes driver-seat state for downstream readers
end note

@enduml
